    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>编年史：中世纪》</strong>带您进入动荡不安的沙盒环境，体验残酷而又美丽的欧洲中世纪世界。从底层起步，仅凭勇气和意志，在遭遇战、野战和攻城战中奋力拼搏，每一场战斗都是迈向更强权势的一步。建造属于您的城堡，抵御来犯的敌人。凭借无情的肉搏能力称霸战场，穿戴精良的装备，调整战术，在战斗中击溃一切阻碍。在这个勃勃生机、万物竞发的国度中塑造您的天命，您的每一个抉择将撼动历史，每一次挥剑都可能改变命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>书写您的故事，铸就您的天命！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸式中世纪沙盒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进充满活力的中世纪欧洲——这个广阔的沙盒世界动荡不安，战火肆虐，联盟更迭。创建属于自己的角色，体验充满冲突与机遇的道路。铸就您的天命，改写历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/3b59ec386509f513a37ffd871ed60146.poster.avif?t=1763475050\" width=1170 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/3b59ec386509f513a37ffd871ed60146.webm?t=1763475050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/3b59ec386509f513a37ffd871ed60146.mp4?t=1763475050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大规模战役</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借技巧与策略，掌握中世纪战争的诀窍。招募士兵，训练军队，率领将士们投入史诗般的战斗。指挥史上有名的劲旅，例如目光敏锐的英格兰长弓手，或是势不可挡的法国骑兵。在战斗中发号施令，还可以与好友一起在自定义战役中并肩作战。洞察战局，果断决策——一击制胜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/559aaae32990e429d7cb747415cb3400.poster.avif?t=1763475050\" width=1170 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/559aaae32990e429d7cb747415cb3400.webm?t=1763475050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/559aaae32990e429d7cb747415cb3400.mp4?t=1763475050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >您的选择，您的旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个中世纪沙盒世界中书写您的传奇故事，每一个决定都至关重要。选择权力、冒险或财富，通过和平外交或武力冲突来创造只属于您的故事。您的胜利之路从这里开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/36e5ea112ceb21ec4e9b1505d02048a4.poster.avif?t=1763475050\" width=1170 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/36e5ea112ceb21ec4e9b1505d02048a4.webm?t=1763475050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/36e5ea112ceb21ec4e9b1505d02048a4.mp4?t=1763475050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个不断演变的美丽世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验由尖端技术打造的精美中世纪欧洲。我们的游戏将不断进步，根据社区反馈打造出鲜活的中世纪游乐场——玩家可以在这里书写自己的故事，而且绝对不会出现雷同的情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/6be0ed1d73f51b4a9b3b4ca503d0e1ee.poster.avif?t=1763475050\" width=1170 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/6be0ed1d73f51b4a9b3b4ca503d0e1ee.webm?t=1763475050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231020/extras/6be0ed1d73f51b4a9b3b4ca503d0e1ee.mp4?t=1763475050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
